text: Sven Schwarz (born 3 December 1964) is a Dutch rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haarlem
